<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.8">
<l>iṟukku miṟaiyiṟuttuṇṇa vevvula kukkuntaṉ mūrtti</l>
<l>niṟuttiṉāṉ ṟeyvaṅka ḷāka vatteyva nāyakaṉ ṟāṉē</l>
<l>maṟuttiru mārva ṉavaṉṟaṉ pūtaṅkaḷ kītaṅkaḷ pāṭi</l>
<l>veṟuppiṉṟi ñālattu mikkār mēvit toḻutuymmi ṉīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who stays, since he stays [and] absorbs, he is the form of all the worlds.</l>
<l>As he established the gods, he is the leader of those gods.</l>
<l>The bhūtas of him on whose chest Śrī is a stain sing songs</l>
<l>[and] without displeasure increase in the world. Joining [and] worshipping [them] be saved, you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
